大約三分之一的安哥拉人都生活在羅安達，其中53%處於貧困線之下，因而大多數人的生活條件也很差，電力和水資源依舊短缺，交通狀況也堪憂<ref>[http://www.dfid.gov.uk/Media-Room/Case-Studies/2009/Keeping-the-flow-in-Angolas-slums/ Keeping the flow in Angola's slums] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090715122124/http://www.dfid.gov.uk/Media-Room/Case-Studies/2009/Keeping-the-flow-in-Angolas-slums/ |date=2009-07-15 }}, Department for International Development (DFID), United Kingdom (February 13, 2009)</ref>。而另一方面，少數富有者卻建造了很多奢華的建築。對外國人來說，羅安達是世界上[[外派員工生活費用最昂貴城市列表|生活費用最昂貴城市]]之一<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mercer.com/costoflivingpr |title=Worldwide Cost of Living survey 2010 - City rankings |publisher=www.mercer.com |date= |accessdate=2010-06-29 |archive-date=2011-07-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110725215323/http://www.mercer.com/costoflivingpr |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2014年3月採用新的進口關稅，而物價更是飛漲。半升香草冰激凌的價格可達31美元，實際上，從蒜到汽車價格無一不高。雖然初衷是保護本地工業和農業，但實際上這種高關稅只造成了人民生活困苦。<ref name="www.independent.co.uk">{{cite news|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/africa/angolas-new-import-tariffs-putting-the-squeeze-on-the-poorest-residents-in-one-of-the-worlds-most-expensive-cities-9278530.html|title=Angola's new import tariffs putting the squeeze on the poorest residents in one of the world's most expensive cities|publisher=The Independent|date=2014-04-23|accessdate=2014-05-02|archive-date=2014-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140427052726/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/africa/angolas-new-import-tariffs-putting-the-squeeze-on-the-poorest-residents-in-one-of-the-worlds-most-expensive-cities-9278530.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

製造業主要生產便利食品、飲料、織物和衣物、水泥的等建築材料、塑料產品、金屬器皿、香煙等。羅安達有石油精煉廠，雖然石油工廠在內戰中受到破壞，石油業從業人員工資仍然高達平均工資的20倍，為5400美元<ref name="www.independent.co.uk"/>。羅安達港是天然港，主要在此出口咖啡、棉花、糖、鑽石、鐵和鹽等，隨著經濟發展，建築業日益興隆。<ref name="economist.com">{{cite news |url=http://www.economist.com/displaystory.cfm?story_id=10316212 |title=GDP growth: A look ahead |publisher=The Economist |date=2007-12-19 |accessdate=2010-06-28 |archive-date=2010-01-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100125213302/http://www.economist.com/displaystory.cfm?story_id=10316212 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==交通==
羅安達是[[羅安達鐵路|羅安達鐵路]]的起始點，這條鐵路通往東部的[[馬蘭哲|馬蘭哲]]。內戰期間鐵路被毀，但現在經過修復已經可以重新通往馬蘭哲了<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.chinainternationalfund.com/projects1.asp?Id=284 |title=China International Fund Limited |publisher=Chinainternationalfund.com |date= |accessdate=2010-06-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090618030958/http://www.chinainternationalfund.com/projects1.asp?Id=284 |archive-date=2009-06-18 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。不同於鐵路，羅安達的公路較為破敗，政府正在修繕中。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://allafrica.com/stories/200808180008.html |title=Angola: Part of Luanda's Highway Complete By December |publisher=allAfrica.com |date=2008-08-15 |accessdate=2010-06-28 |archive-date=2009-10-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091004173236/http://allafrica.com/stories/200808180008.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

羅安達的主要機場為[[二月四日國際機場|二月四日國際機場]]，此機場也是安哥拉最大的機場。新的國際機場[[安哥拉國際機場|安哥拉國際機場]]的第一期工程已在2010年完工<ref>[http://jornaldeangola.sapo.ao/20/0/novo_aeroporto_orgulha_africa Novo aeroporto orgulha África]{{dead link|date=2018年4月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }} Jornal de Angola Online, 12 May 2012 (en)</ref>，本来預計2015/2016年即可交付使用<ref>[http://www.aeroscope.de/magazin-nachrichten/items/taag-durchstarter-aus-angola#.UFxb6Y2TuV9 Interview with Pimentel Araujo about the Angola air traffic] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131203073144/http://www.aeroscope.de/magazin-nachrichten/items/taag-durchstarter-aus-angola |date=2013-12-03 }}, aeroscope.com, 21 August 2012 (de)</ref>，但因資金糾紛而延期至2020年左右<ref>[https://macauhub.com.mo/2017/10/31/pt-novo-aeroporto-internacional-de-luanda-angola-em-funcionamento-em-20192020/ New Luanda international airport in Angola expected to start operating in 2019/2020] {{Wayback|url=https://macauhub.com.mo/2017/10/31/pt-novo-aeroporto-internacional-de-luanda-angola-em-funcionamento-em-20192020/ |date=20210208172721 }}, 2017-11-01</ref>。羅安達港是安哥拉最大的港口，大部分的進出進口貿易都在此完成，其規模也在擴大。

